column2: Lotto Men Kochi Tuskers Authentic Orange Jersey
column24:
• Product Description
  • Style Note

  • Crank up your style as the cricket craze kicks off this summer with this Kochi Tuskers Authentic Tee Jersey from Lotto. You'll be displaying team pride with this jersey as you cheer your favourite players at the IPL. There's no better way of saying 'Go Tuskers!' than with this jersey!

  • Product Details

  • Orange and purple jersey made of 100% polyester
column28:
Kochi Tuskers logo on left chest and branding on back and sleeves

  • Material & Care

  • 100% polyester
    Machine wash in lukewarm water below 40 degrees
column29:
using a mild detergent
Wash dark colours separately
Do not soak
column32:
dry clean or iron on print/trims/ logo
Dry in shade
Warm iron
